    .card-body
      h5.card-title Garage Sale App
      p.card-text Simple app to help sell your stuff. Inventory/Item management, payments integration, item bid/reservation, viewing appointment scheduling and announcements. Virtual or not.
  .card
    // img(src="./projects/favicon.ico" class="card-img-top" alt="Project 6")
    .card-body
      h5.card-title Alexa skills - Eskom load-shedding shedules
      .card-text
        p.
          Living in South Africa, we're painfully aware of living with water and electricity constraints.
          For electricity, there are various mobile apps that provide us with the schedule that is published by the main provider, Eskom.
          Alexa doesn't have that skill right now so this is a great option for me to to dig into Alexa skills.
  .card
